track_notes: Park at the large parking area for the Clan burial site at NG 946 212. Go across the road through a gate.  Follow the straightforward track up to the col at NG 956 229. Turn west and head for the obvious summit ridge ahead. Outflank the rocky ridge on the right (north side) to reach the summit ridge. Continue to trig point, good antenna support. Unusually good path for a Corbett.
